b'Strawberry anything\xe2\x80\xa6 the fruit, strawberry fillings, strawberry cake. Now here she is turning 7 & still loving & requesting her strawberries!!!\xf0\x9f\x8d\x93\xe2\x9d\xa4\xef\xb8\x8f\xf0\x9f\x8d\x93\xe2\x9d\xa4\xef\xb8\x8f\xf0\x9f\x8d\x93\xe2\x9d\xa4\xef\xb8\x8f\xf0\x9f\x98\x8d #AskX'
b'It\xe2\x80\x99s cute she wants a strawberry birthday \xe2\x80\x94 coming full circle as her mom, it\xe2\x80\x99s the one prominent thing she had me craving while I was pregnant with her. #AskX'

b'Our family is big on a theme! \nIt\xe2\x80\x99s been everything from dinosaurs to Roblox to Parkour (she\xe2\x80\x99s into it like her brother was)\xe2\x80\xa6and she finally arrived at a strawberry\xf0\x9f\x8d\x93themed party.\nThe hardest thing has been sourcing a strawberry bouncy house\xf0\x9f\xa4\x94\xf0\x9f\xa4\xaf #AskX'
b'Summer has already changed the theme of her birthday at least 10 times through the year. #AskX https://t.co/D2CVPgVIEv'
b'Playing with saturated pops of color to more grainy black & white moods\xe2\x80\xa6all of it was a work of art.\nA take on old pin up art of that era - I got to play dress up every day! #AskX'
b'Ellen von Unwerth helped me create the most epic and fun artwork for this album. She tapped into the play and classic feel of what the spirit of this genre/era and world meant to me. #AskX'

b'And then the video I co-directed with Floria Sigismondi for Hurt\xe2\x80\xa6and then on tour with my incredible team of dancers who helped me create & embody the live version \xe2\x80\x94 bringing circus elements & acrobatics to life!\nIt was a fun dream to live out! #AskX'
b'The throwback circus theme on disk 2 was a very cool world I loved diving into with Linda on the intro song \xe2\x80\x9cWelcome\xe2\x80\x9d #AskX'
b'I loved working with DJ Premier and Linda Perry \xe2\x80\x94 embodying 2 different musical worlds, but exploring the same theme for me from disk 1 to 2. #AskX'

b'Authenticity was something you couldn\xe2\x80\x99t fake back then.\nIntegrity means everything to me. There are so many special stories and meaningful moments pieced  together within these records.\nFurther dissection for another time\xe2\x80\xa6. #AskX'

b'And it\xe2\x80\x99s sad that much of it gets lost or unheard through generations. So it was and is very important to me to always shed light & appreciation for all who came before and keep their spirits & work alive. #AskX'
b'There is so much incredible art and so many stories, talent, voices, musicianship and creativity that pushed boundaries and paved the way for artists today. #AskX'
b'The videos & artwork were so personal to me \xe2\x80\x94 appreciating and embodying the classic old Hollywood cinema feel that has also visually inspired me. #AskX'
b'Looking back, it was brave to make a double album of material when in pop it\xe2\x80\x99s encouraged to simply keep it simple and churn it out. #AskX'

b'It was a tribute record for me to pay a personal nod to the great artists & originators of music \xe2\x80\x94 from soul to blues to jazz & beyond \xe2\x80\x94 that greatly influenced me as a young girl & impacted how I not only listen to music, but more importantly how I FEEL it. #AskX'
b'Looking back on this album, I am so proud of this specific body of work for so many reasons! #AskX https://t.co/XSP3aUR0z0'
b'The classic holiday movies\xe2\x80\xa6the stores filling in with seasonal decor\xe2\x80\xa6Starbucks holiday flavors\xe2\x80\xa6theme parties\xe2\x80\xa6I can go on & on. #AskX'

b'I love jacket weather\xe2\x80\xa6cozy sweaters, fireplaces, hot chocolate, pumpkins, fall/holiday colors\xe2\x80\xa6festivities\xe2\x80\xa6decorating the house\xe2\x80\xa6getting silly\xe2\x80\xa6family fun time\xe2\x80\xa6ALL of it! #AskX'

b'Every year come mid to late JULY I start already getting excited about \xe2\x80\x9cHalloween/holiday\xe2\x80\x9d time around the corner!\nNothing is like the feeling of fall/October into November & then birthday/Xmas time!! It\xe2\x80\x99s my favorite! #AskX https://t.co/UiFAfUvMRB'
b'\xe2\x80\xa6From Genie to the chaps/Dirrty era to the throwback stylistic/classic Back 2 Basics era to Bionic and so on. #AskX'

b'And yes I keep a collection of tour merchandise through the years & product \xe2\x80\x94 I\xe2\x80\x99m in the process of properly archiving things. It\xe2\x80\x99s fun to look back on different chapters of your life through clothing & videos & performances\xe2\x80\xa6 #AskX'
b'Wow the kitty cat lunchbox and Xtina Skechers take me BACK!\nIt\xe2\x80\x99s endearing to see and appreciate the reminders of past childhood work and beyond. #AskX https://t.co/1ZVVYV20pc'
b'Etta James- my favorite singer ever- would have been great to be on a record with.\nNina Simone\xe2\x80\xa6Janis Joplin\xe2\x80\xa6list goes on #AskX'

b'Whitney, so epic and one of my first inspirations. Amy Winehouse would have been incredible to collaborate with.\nIn history, Billie Holiday was incredible and an original female groundbreaker\xe2\x80\xa6 #AskX'
b'There are so many that passed far too soon!\nThe list of dream collabs could go on forever\xe2\x80\xa6 #AskX https://t.co/8HiDa9aViT'

b'To a woman who has worked under conditions and pressure unimaginable to most, I promise you she deserves all of the freedom possible to live her happiest life.\n\nMy heart goes out to Britney.\xc2\xa0She deserves all the TRUE love and support in the world. \xf0\x9f\xa4\x8d'
b'The conviction and desperation of this plea for freedom leads me to believe that this person I once knew has been living without compassion or decency from those in control.'

b'While I am not behind the closed doors of this very layered & personal yet public conversation \xe2\x80\x93 all I can do is share from my heart on what I\xe2\x80\x99ve heard, read and seen in the media.'
b'Every woman must have the right to her own body, her own reproductive system, her own privacy, her own space, her own healing and her own happiness.'

b'To be silenced, ignored, bullied or denied support by those \xe2\x80\x9cclose\xe2\x80\x9d to you is the most depleting, devastating and demeaning thing imaginable.\xc2\xa0The harmful mental and emotional damage this can take on a human spirit is nothing to be taken lightly.'

b'These past few days I\xe2\x80\x99ve been thinking about Britney and everything she is going through. \n\nIt is unacceptable that any woman, or human, wanting to be in control of their own destiny might not be allowed to live life as they wish. https://t.co/NRhNwcJaD3'
